Synopsis:
The movie revolves around Appa Thosar (Vikram Gokhle) and his grandson Vakratund Thosar (Archit Dewadhar) and their bonding with a thread of Mathematics. The movie has beautifully bloomed with various emotions of love, relations, family, principles and faith. Each elements enacted by the actors in this movie are beyond words and limit.
